"           STROKE OVERVIEW",
"          </a>",
"         </li>",
"         <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"          <a href=\"#H2\">",
"           WHAT IS A HEMORRHAGIC STROKE?",
"          </a>",
"         </li>",
